https://docs.spring.io/spring-boot/docs/2.1.4.RELEASE/maven-plugin/examples/repackage-classifier.html

&gt; Maven Plugin &lt;br/&gt;
&gt; The finalName property is no longer customizable to align
&gt; with the behavior of standard Maven plugins.
&gt; 
&gt; If you were customizing the repackage goal, **the main execution has now
&gt; an id of repackage that must be specified**, see the updated sample.

It is simple, just add the `&lt;id&gt;repackage&lt;/id&gt;` to the file `src/monitoring/pom.xml`, then it will work

