I don&#39;t recommend loading the file in the `static` initializer.

This way, snakeyaml creates and instance of `Settings` which throws a `NullPointerException` because of the statement in the constructor.

I suggest this:

```
public class Settings {
    private final static InputStream file;
    private final static Settings parsedSettings;
