Because your Global variable `private ArrayList&lt;Breaker&gt; listBreaker;` is never assigned to the new list it stays `NULL`.


In your `onCreate` you&#39;re just assigning `List&lt;Breaker&gt; listBreaker = new ArrayList&lt;Breaker&gt;();` new object to another list.

Instead it should be as following:

    
    listPanel = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;();
    listBlock = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;();
    listBreaker = new ArrayList&lt;Breaker&gt;();


For more info on Null pointers: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/218384/what-is-a-nullpointerexception-and-how-do-i-fix-it

